{
  "info": {
    "name": "JTL ERP Cloud API - LIVE Production",
    "description": "## LIVE Production API - Real Data\n\n**This collection queries the REAL JTL ERP Cloud GraphQL API.**\n\n### API Endpoints\n- **Auth:** `https://auth.jtl-cloud.com/oauth2/token`\n- **GraphQL:** `https://api.jtl-cloud.com/erp/v2/graphql`\n\n### Tenant\n- **Company:** Sportbedarf Sommer GmbH\n- **Tenant ID:** `16eff290-3d20-4d32-8387-39e6e5c27506`\n\n### Data Summary\n- 164 Sales Orders\n- 110 Customers\n- 661 Products\n- 70 Invoices\n\n### Authentication\nOAuth 2.0 Client Credentials flow with JWT Bearer token.\n\n---\n*JTL Hackathon 2026*",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Get Access Token",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
              "console.log(\"Token saved!\");"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "urlencoded",
          "urlencoded": [
            {
              "key": "grant_type",
              "value": "client_credentials",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{auth_url}}",
          "host": ["{{auth_url}}"]
        },
        "auth": {
          "type": "basic",
          "basic": [
            {
              "key": "username",
              "value": "{{client_id}}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "key": "password",
              "value": "{{client_secret}}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "## LIVE Production Auth\n\nAuthenticates against **https://auth.jtl-cloud.com** (REAL JTL Cloud).\n\nToken is automatically saved to environment variable `access_token`."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Get Tenant Info (Company)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Tenant-ID",
            "value": "{{tenant_id}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"query\": \"query { QueryCompanies(first: 5) { totalCount nodes { id companyName owner street postalCode city country phone emailAddress taxId } } }\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{api_url}}",
          "host": ["{{api_url}}"]
        },
        "description": "## LIVE Production Data\n\nQueries **https://api.jtl-cloud.com/erp/v2/graphql** (REAL JTL ERP API).\n\nReturns company info for tenant: **Sportbedarf Sommer GmbH**\n\nThis proves the API connection is to REAL production data."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Sales Orders (Recent)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Tenant-ID",
            "value": "{{tenant_id}}"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"query\": \"query { QuerySalesOrders(first: 10, order: [{ salesOrderDate: DESC }]) { totalCount nodes { salesOrderNumber salesOrderDate companyName totalGrossAmount currencyIso paymentStatus deliveryStatus } } }\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{api_url}}",
          "host": ["{{api_url}}"]
        },
        "description": "Get 10 most recent sales orders"
      },
      "response": []
    },
